\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Ritter\"}, {\"begin\": 2706, \"end\": 2710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Golf\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.6333476740743753e-13, \"text\": \"Golf\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Golf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Golf\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has more than 20 years of sports media experience, and previously was the general manager at the Morning Read, where he led that business\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s growth and joined SI as part of an acquisition in 2022.\", \"from\": 2712, \"to\": 2912, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier in his career he spent more than a decade at SI and Golf Magazine, and his journalism awards include a MIN Magazine Award and an Edward R. Murrow Award for sports reporting.\", \"from\": 2913, \"to\": 3094, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2973, \"end\": 2986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Golf_Magazine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Golf Magazine\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Golf_Magazine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Golf_Magazine\"}, {\"begin\": 3024, \"end\": 3027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota_Wild\", \"score\": 0.6246137870867573, \"rank\": 0.6001739065109215, \"text\": \"MIN\", \"types\": [\"Q4498974\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota_Wild\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota_Wild\"}, {\"begin\": 3060, \"end\": 3066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Edward_R._Murrow\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0272671794615546e-27, \"text\": \"Murrow\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Edward_R._Murrow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Edward_R._Murrow\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He received a bachelor\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s degree from the University of Michigan and a master\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s from Northwestern University\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Medill School of Journalism.\", \"from\": 3095, \"to\": 3239, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00c2\\u00a9 2026ABG-SI LLC-SPORTS ILLUSTRATED IS A REGISTERED TRADEMARK OF ABG-SI LLC.\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3318, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"- All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 3319, \"to\": 3341, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The content on this site is for entertainment and educational purposes only.\", \"from\": 3342, \"to\": 3418, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Betting and gambling content is intended for individuals 21+ and is based on individual commentators' opinions and not that of Sports Illustrated or its affiliates, licensees and related brands.\", \"from\": 3419, \"to\": 3613, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3546, \"end\": 3564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6717420817060704e-13, \"text\": \"Sports Illustrated\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All picks and predictions are suggestions only and not a guarantee of success or profit.\", \"from\": 3614, \"to\": 3702, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you or someone you know has a gambling problem, crisis counseling and referral services can be accessed by calling 1-800-GAMBLER.\", \"from\": 3703, \"to\": 3835, \"entities\": []}]}"